      <figcaption><span style="font-size: 0.9em; font-family: Times New Roman;">Juggluco
          Wear</span></figcaption> </figure>
    <figure> <img src="alarms.png" style="object-fit:contain;height:4.5cm; width:auto;">
      <figcaption><span style="font-size: 0.9em; font-family: Times New Roman;">Specify
